posts.post_title: FS Got a couple of PSA graded T206 Im looking to sell
posts.post_content:
I’m not sure what these are worth so if you’re interested make me an offer! This is my first post on this site. I’ve been looking and reading it seems like a very nice place! Let me know if you’re interested!

I have a PSA 5 MK Wid Conroy/Piedmont and a PSA 4 MC Frank Owen/Sweet Caporal/Charles Bray Collection!

These cards have been listed in the auction thread at a starting Bid of $80 a piece! Head over there if you’re interested!
I can’t figure out how to post pictures on here so message me if you’re interested in seeing pictures haha
If you post what you have with prices that would probably help people know if they have any interest.  Good luck with the sale!
